[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/blackwood"]
[Student "S"]
{Your 3\H bid showed 11-12 points. Decide how you would answer partner's Blackwood 4NT, then click on <b>BID</b> above. 

The Blackwood response for 1 Ace is 5\D. Partner evidently was hoping for 2, and he signs off at 5\H. He is the Captain so you pass.}

